{
  "stem": "2713.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't, because they-- they couldn't travel on a train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were just risking their lives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Cracow, a policeman stopped them, a Polish policeman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, what are you looking at?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that was the ghetto there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're just looking at things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he just let them go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they came to Dzialoszyce.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were the happiest people in the world, because the whole family was together again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not comfortable, but-- but everybody was happy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It doesn't matter where we slept or so, but we were all together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only one person who wasn't with us was the oldest brother, because he was in the army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it didn't take long, and he came home, as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They let him go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came back, so we were the whole family, and we were happy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But unfortunately, we were happy, but, every day, it was getting worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was impossible to live, the way the Germans were going on with things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, every day, there are new orders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I don't know if you heard, there was a Judenrat, which-- a Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans used to give them orders, what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Today, for example, they want a kilo of gold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if not, they will kill so and so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and they used to work, they-- they ask every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And things were getting impossible to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they stopped you from going outside the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were not allowed to go outside the city at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we took a risk.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
